      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Did you install `vcpkg` and the dependencies as per the [instructions](https://github.com/bitcoin/bitcoin/tree/master/build_msvc)? The `db.h` and `db_cxx.h` files are in the `vckg\\installed\\x64-windows-static\\include` directory.\r\n\r\nIf you did then the next thing is to double check you've set the `Platform` in Visual Studio to match your vcpkg triplet. For example if your vcpkg triplet is `x64-windows-static` you need to make sure you are doing an x64 platform build in Visual Studio.",
